  "subtitle": "Spanish vegetable paella with peppers, artichokes, and saffron",
  "excerpt": "Vegetable paella is a Spanish rice dish of peppers, artichoke hearts, tomatoes, and beans in saffron-steeped stock. Without the distraction of meat or fish, the flavour rests entirely on the sofrito, the stock, and the caramelised socarrat base. A good vegetable paella is as satisfying as any meat version.",
