    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Vegetable paella is built on the same method as any other paella: a deep "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "socarrat",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termSlug": "socarrat"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " on the base, a properly reduced sofrito, and rice cooked without stirring. The peppers and artichokes go in the oil first, so they caramelise before the rice is added."
          }
        ]
      },
